## 2. Purpose / Description (for your email / form)

> **BotTest Buddy** helps RPA developers quickly create structured test cases, test data sets, and UAT checklists for UiPath automations.
>
> Users can paste a process description, PDD snippet, or Studio/StudioX workflow summary, and the GPT generates:
>
> * Happy-path, negative and boundary test scenarios
> * Step-by-step test cases in tabular form
> * Suggested test data combinations
> * Edge cases and exception scenarios to validate bot robustness

This reduces manual effort in writing test cases and helps standardise QA across all RPA projects.

